title: PC CRT Monitor Electrical Drawings Diagrams Schematics
description:
PC CRT Monitors - Electrical Drawings Diagrams collection - MrCyberdude also included a DjVu Viewer

CRT (Cathode Ray tube) monitors are a dying breed now and it is getting harder to find someone to repair them. Hope you find this of interest.

I had my crt monitor which happened to be a Sony G520 die on me when it was 2 years old.
I wasn't happy about that and to make matters worse i wasn't prepared to then fork out for someone to tell me what was wrong with it.

The original site info is contained within the torrent.

I think i have the following schematics within....! LET ME KNOW IF NOT and Please ADD any sites you know about... Thanks
